function* simpleGenerator(){
    console.log("Before 1")
    yield 1
    console.log("After 1")
    console.log("Before 2")
    yield 2
    console.log("After 2")
    console.log("Before 3")
    yield 3
    console.log("After 3")
}
const generatorObject = simpleGenerator()
const obj = generatorObject.next()
console.log(generatorObject.next())
console.log(generatorObject.next())
console.log(generatorObject.next())
